name: trumped.ai
description: Trumped.ai allows users to easily generate and share AI videos of Trump. There's really not much more to say about it than that. It's a simple product but built on fairly robust architecture. The coin associated with it $trumped.ai, is a meme coin. The team is lean and building out simple functionality. The goal of the product is to get people to laugh. We are adding content moderation to the video creation, amongst other features. It's a good product. Try it out!
